for monitoring purpose.

commit.message:
Allow Emitter to use a custom ExecutorService (close #278)

This commit allows a user to use its own ExecutorService in the Emitter
to have a more granular control over threads created by an Emitter.

Co-authored-by: Paul Laturaze <paul.laturaze@zivver.com>
